=head1 DESCRIPTION

Contains a map of variables in a prompt from Prompt management to an
object containing the values to fill in for them when running model
invocation. For more information, see How Prompt management works
(https://docs.aws.amazon.com/bedrock/latest/userguide/prompt-management-how.html).

